Horse Race Notes:
4 horses
each horse has a name
horse 1 is your horse (Golden_Nugget)
3 villian horses (Bad_Boy, Raggy_Runner, Mean_and_Sneaky)
every user input causes a random advance of the horses
horses will move a random amount of spaces on their own

your horse will move a random number 1-4, finish line = 20
motivation codes double the value or auto win
special patterns are typed "asdi" is a motivation code


horse race will be a class
horses must all be a class

villian class?

minimum of one horse class 